    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine. This high-revving power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Performance-critical maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains composed thanks to refreshed bushings and a precise steering rack. While the vehicle exhibits minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle mapping remain sharp. This is a mechanically robust example of the E46 platform, optimized for the purist who values tactile feedback and atmospheric induction.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
