    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, an atmospheric masterpiece utilizing eight individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. This unit delivers a linear power band peaking at an 8,400 RPM redline, mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The rear-end features the GKN-sourced M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal traction through corner exit. The chassis remains composed with EDC-equipped dampers and factory-spec subframe bushings. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the critical rod bearing replacement and throttle valve actuators. While showing minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the carbon fiber roof retains its structural integrity and the interior bolsters show minimal compression. A mechanically robust example for the purist enthusiast.",
